title: Dalian ir'Tain II
text:
Lord Dalian ir'Tain II, head of [[Sharn]]'s illustrious [[ir'Tain family]], is said to have perished in a shipwreck during the end of the [[Last War]]. The ship supposedly went down deep in the territory of the [[sahuagin]], but Lord ir'Tain's body was never recovered. Rumors abound that ir'Tain is still aliveâ€”that he is a pirate captain, a prisoner of the sahuagin, or the prince of a lost kingdom in the jungles of [[Xen'drik]],
depending on which tale you believe.
